products.title: Spirit Mulberry Venetian Blind - 25mm Slat
products.metadescription: The spirit mulberry aluminium venetian blind is light, gorgeous and an elegant choice if you're looking to add a bit of colour to your home.   This blind will give your home a most delectable and tranquil setting both day and night. The smooth matte slats are also easy to clean,
